  07 Apr 2005; Simon Stelling <blubb@gentoo.org> aterm-0.4.2-r11.ebuild:
  stable on amd64

  07 Apr 2005; Michał Januszewski <spock@gentoo.org>
  aterm-1.00_beta2.ebuild:
  Fixed the dependency on afterstep. Aterm-1.00 will not work properly with
  afterstep < 2.00.

  14 Feb 2005; Michał Januszewski <spock@gentoo.org>
  aterm-0.4.2-r11.ebuild, aterm-0.4.2-r12.ebuild, aterm-0.4.2-r7.ebuild,
  aterm-0.4.2-r9.ebuild:
  Removed references to 'macos'.

