  Stable on alpha.

  07 Feb 2005; Sven Wegener <swegener@gentoo.org> aterm-0.4.2-r11.ebuild,
  aterm-0.4.2-r12.ebuild, aterm-0.4.2-r7.ebuild, aterm-0.4.2-r9.ebuild:
